data.name: lblUsageInfo.Text
data.value: Move to any open application(s), select some text you would like to save somewhere, and hit the clipping hotkey displayed above to save the text you've selected in the general list of clipped texts. You can also change the hotkey by clicking on the 'Change Clipping Hotkey' button then from the dialog displayed hit any set of keys you'd wish to use, then click 'Save && Close'.
